* Major changes in 1.1 (For upgrade user from 1.0, please see UPGRADE_1.1)

- Anti-CSRFattack.
- Improve output: include AtomAPI and RSS.
- Plural authours can write articles.
- Page cache. It reduce ruby process and DB load.
- Gzip encode transfer.
- Improve anti-spam for comment and trackback.
- Browser side cache control by Cache-Control: and Last-Modified: headers.
- You can activate/deactivate blog ping destinations.
- Send notify mail when comment or trackback is added.
